Privacy Policy

Effective Date: [Insert Date]

1. Introduction
Welcome to Direct Resell, a Discord bot designed to facilitate interactions between users for the purpose of trading various items and services on Discord servers. At Direct Resell, we value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information.

This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your personal information. By using our services, you agree to the terms and practices described in this policy.

2. Information We Collect
We may collect and process the following personal information when you use our service:

User-Provided Information: This includes the data you provide when using our service, such as your Discord username and server interactions.

Automatically Collected Information: We may collect data on how you use our service, including server interactions and communications.

Server Information: We may collect information about the Discord servers where our bot is installed.

3. How We Use Your Information
We use your information for the following purposes:

Providing and Improving our Service: We use your data to deliver, maintain, and enhance our service.

Communications: We may contact you with service-related messages, updates, and promotions.

Analyzing Usage: We analyze user interactions to understand how our service is used and to improve its performance.

4. Data Sharing and Disclosure
We do not share your personal information except in the following circumstances:

With Your Consent: We may share your data after obtaining your consent to do so.

For Legal Reasons: We may share your information to comply with legal obligations.

5. Security
We employ appropriate security measures to safeguard your data. However, no data transmission or storage system is entirely secure.

6. Data Retention
We retain your data only for as long as necessary to provide our services and as required by law.

7. Your Rights
You have the right to access, rectify, erase, or object to the processing of your personal data. To exercise these rights, please contact us.

8. Changes to this Policy
We may modify this Privacy Policy periodically. When we do, we will update the Effective Date.

9. Contact Us
For any questions or concerns regarding this Privacy Policy, please contact 'iamfabar' on Discord or open a ticket on our support server: 'https://discord.gg/bSnXy4gMn3'.
